org.apache.iceberg.exceptions

Interface CleanableFailure

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BadRequestException, CherrypickAncestorCommitException, CommitFailedException, DuplicateWAPCommitException, ForbiddenException, NoSuchIcebergTableException, NoSuchNamespaceException, NoSuchTableException, NoSuchViewException, NotAuthorizedException, ServiceUnavailableException, ValidationException

    public interface CleanableFailure
    A marker interface for commit exceptions where the state is known to be failure and uncommitted metadata can be cleaned up.
